r old issues\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:08:17Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:08:17Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"d7aa61e6f1ef808b1817160fb4f3b2d8bec7023c\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/d7aa61e6f1ef808b1817160fb4f3b2d8bec7023c\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Add script to backfill duplicate comments for old issues\\\\n\\\\nCreates a script that identifies old issues without duplicate detection comments and triggers the existing claude-dedupe-issues workflow for each one. This helps ensure historical issues get proper duplicate detection coverage.\\\\n\\\\nFeatures:\\\\n- Scans issues from configurable time period (default 30 days)\\\\n- Skips issues that already have duplicate detection comments\\\\n- Triggers existing workflow instead of duplicating logic\\\\n- Includes dry-run mode and rate limiting for safety\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:03:40Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:06:36Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"072856dd5b7740cc2cae1c0ed3b7c10633632e15\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/072856dd5b7740cc2cae1c0ed3b7c10633632e15\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge pull request #5411 from anthropics/boris/gity\\\\n\\\\nUpdate auto-close-duplicates script to actually close issues\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T18:54:07Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T18:54:07Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"1cc90e9b788c47fafaac31b09ee8d3407775d8d6\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/1cc90e9b788c47fafaac31b09ee8d3407775d8d6\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Update auto-close-duplicates script to actually close issues\\\\n\\\\n- Remove dry run mode and implement actual issue closing\\\\n- Extract duplicate issue number from bot comments\\\\n- Close issues via GitHub API with proper state and comments\\\\n- Add error handling for API failures\\\\n- Use Claude Code comment format with reopening instructions\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@ant