uthor\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"1579216fc7fd9052f338b06c1dcf471ad70605d0\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/1579216fc7fd9052f338b06c1dcf471ad70605d0\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Enable auto-close duplicate issues workflow\\\\n\\\\nRemove DRY RUN from workflow name and description to activate the automatic closing of duplicate issues after the testing period.\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T21:03:43Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T21:03:43Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"f0042afb3bf31aa7ea2613374e3210bc6015884d\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/f0042afb3bf31aa7ea2613374e3210bc6015884d\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Replace lock-threads action with GitHub Script (#5330)\\\\n\\\\nReplaces the dessant/lock-threads action with a direct GitHub Script\\\\nimplementation to avoid the deprecated search/issues API endpoint warning.\\\\nThe new implementation:\\\\n- Uses github.rest.issues.listForRepo() instead of the deprecated search API\\\\n- Maintains the same 7-day inactivity threshold\\\\n- Adds the same comment before locking\\\\n- Uses 'resolved' as the lock reason\\\\n- Handles pagination properly for large repositories\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-authored-by: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Ashwin Bhat\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"ashwin@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T20:02:20Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T20:02:20Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"ashwin-ant\\\",\\\"id\\\":178951676,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/ashwin-ant\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/178951676?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"6059607354e01ee31d7e5f1c7068298bd8d52d40\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/6059607354e01ee31d7e5f1c7068298bd8d52d40\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge pull request #5420 from anthropics/boris/cmyy\\\\n\\\\nFix workflow failure by adding workflow_dispatch trigger\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:57:16Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:57:16Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"478f63be73f911a0dbe2b16f5749ed38de6cbb64\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/478f63be73f911a0dbe2b16f5749ed38de6cbb64\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Fix workflow failure by adding workflow_dispatch trigger\\\\n\\\\nThe backfill-duplicate-comments script was failing because it tried to trigger\\\\nclaude-dedupe-issues.yml via workflow_dispatch, but that workflow only had an\\\\nissues trigger. Added workflow_dispatch with issue_number input and updated the\\\\nprompt to use either event or input issue number.\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:55:48Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:55:48Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"a7edbdc9e7f4a96175f80084bb3da1f4a0d9d3d5\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/a7edbdc9e7f4a96175f80084bb3da1f4a0d9d3d5\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge pull request #5414 from anthropics/boris/aier\\\\n\\\\nAdd workflow to backfill duplicate comments\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:13:19Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:13:19Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"399a7dcf2f024e21a93064e047c80af61e2f7d0d\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/399a7dcf2f024e21a93064e047c80af61e2f7d0d\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Add workflow to backfill duplicate comments\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:11:08Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:11:08Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"9ced2a347081db0d12787d7e6e8583de545bf30e\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/9ced2a347081db0d12787d7e6e8583de545bf30e\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge pull request #5413 from anthropics/boris/bktr\\\\n\\\\nAdd script to backfill duplicate comments for old issues\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:08:17Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:08:17Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"d7aa61e6f1ef808b1817160fb4f3b2d8bec7023c\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/d7aa61e6f1ef808b1817160fb4f3b2d8bec7023c\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Add script to backfill duplicate comments for old issues\\\\n\\\\nCreates a script that identifies old issues without duplicate detection comments and triggers the existing claude-dedupe-issues workflow for each one. This helps ensure historical issues get proper duplicate detection coverage.\\\\n\\\\nFeatures:\\\\n- Scans issues from configurable time period (default 30 days)\\\\n- Skips issues that already have duplicate detection comments\\\\n- Triggers existing workflow instead of duplicating logic\\\\n- Includes dry-run mode and rate limiting for safety\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\\\\u003e\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:03:40Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T19:06:36Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"072856dd5b7740cc2cae1c0ed3b7c10633632e15\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/072856dd5b7740cc2cae1c0ed3b7c10633632e15\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge pull request #5411 from anthropics/boris/gity\\\\n\\\\nUpdate auto-close-duplicates script to actually close issues\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Boris Cherny\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"boris@anthropic.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T18:54:07Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2025-08-08T18:54:07Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"bcherny\\\",\\\"id\\\":1761758,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/bcherny\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1761758?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/web-flow\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19864447?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"1cc90e9b788c47fafaac31b09ee8d3407775d8d6\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/commit/1cc90e9b788c47fafaac31b09ee8d3407775d8d6\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Update auto-close-duplicates script to actually close issues\\\\n\\\\n- Remove dry run mode and implement actual issue closing\\\\n- Extract duplicate issue number from bot comments\\\\n- Close issues via GitHub API with proper state and comments\\\\n- Add error handling for API failures\\\\n- Use Claude Code comment format with reopening instructions\\\\n\\\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\\\\n\\\\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \\\\u003cnoreply@ant