          "content": "# Claude AI Collaboration Analysis\n\n## Summary Statistics\n\nTotal commits analyzed: 158\nNumber of Claude co-authored commits found: 25\nPercentage of commits with Claude collaboration: 15.82%\nNumber of unique human collaborators who worked with Claude: 6\n\n## Top Claude Collaborators\n\n| Developer | GitHub Username | Claude Collaborations |\n|-----------|----------------|----------------------|\n| Boris Cherny | bcherny | 14 |\n| Ashwin Bhat | ashwin-ant | 5 |\n| Kurt Carpenter | ant-kurt | 3 |\n\n## Methodology\n\nThis analysis examined all commits reachable from the `main` branch. A commit was counted as a Claude collaboration when its commit message contained a `Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>` trailer, matched case-insensitively. Commits with multiple matching Claude trailers were counted once.\n\nHuman collaborators were identified from the primary Git commit author and associated GitHub username for each Claude co-authored commit.\n",
          "path": "CLAUDE_COLLABORATION_ANALYSIS.md"
        }
